lead_paragraph: Leicester City's Shinji Okazaki is so drained when he returns from international duty with Japan he is barely recognizable from the bustling forward that played a key role in their title triumph last season, said manager Claudio Ranieri.

headline.print_headline: Okazaki a Different Player After Japan Duty, Says Ranieri
headline.main: Okazaki a Different Player After Japan Duty, Says Ranieri
